nodes.text: Unidentified Assistant Advisory Undersecretary of Media

An individual served the Corporate Sector Authority as Assistant Advisory Undersecretary of Media. While watching a promotional screening of Who Are You To Accuse Me? in Etti IV's capital city, Mondder, the undersecretary was an individual affected by a terrorist attack by the Duroon Rebels. The individual's life was saved by a Tiss'shar gunslinger named Uul-Rha-Shan.
